        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Web Layout Mode</span> This mode <MadCap:snippetText src="../../XMLEditor/WebLayoutModeDescription.flsnp" /></li>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Web Layout (Tablet)&#160;Mode</span> This mode <MadCap:snippetText src="../../XMLEditor/TabletLayoutMode.flsnp" /></li>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Web Layout (Mobile)&#160;Mode</span> This mode <MadCap:snippetText src="../../XMLEditor/MobileLayoutMode.flsnp" /></li>
